                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَدَمَّرۡنَٰهُمۡ﴾: فَأَهْلَكْناهُم.</h2>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "25:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ءَايَةٗ﴾: عِبْرةً.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَأَعۡتَدۡنَا﴾: هَيَّأنا.</h2>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "25:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَأَصۡحَٰبَ ٱلرَّسِّ﴾: أصْحابَ البِئْرِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَقُرُونَۢا﴾: وأُمَماً.</h2>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "25:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ضَرَبۡنَا لَهُ ٱلۡأَمۡثَٰلَ﴾: بَيَّنّا لجَمِيعِ الأُمَمِ الحُجَجَ، وأَزَلْنا عَنْهم الشُّبُهَاتِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿تَبَّرۡنَا﴾: أهْلَكْنا.</h2>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "25:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱلۡقَرۡيَةِ﴾: هي «سَدُومُ» قَرْيَةُ قَومِ لُوطٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مَطَرَ ٱلسَّوۡءِ﴾: أي: بالحِجارةِ مِنَ السَّماءِ.</h2>\n<p>﴿لَا يَرۡجُونَ نُشُورٗا﴾: لا يتَوَقَّعُونَ بَعْثاً بَعْدَ الموتِ.</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "25:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
